separate tickets to your kitchen printer.</p></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4"><div class="feature three"><i class="fa fa-lock"></i><p>1stPayPOS utilizes end-to-end encryption to keep your data secure.</p></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4"><div class="feature four"><i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i><p>1stPayPOS has an integrated employee timeclock.</p></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4"><div class="feature five"><i class="fa fa-wrench"></i><p>24/7 Support to ensure your system stays up and running without downtime.</p></div></div><div class="col-xs-12"><a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary green">Get Started</a></div></div><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12"><h3>FAQ:</h3><div class="panel-group" id="accordion" role="tablist" aria-multiselectable="true"><div class="panel panel-default"><div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading1"><h4 class="panel-title"><a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse1" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse1">What does the 1stPayPOS cost?</a></h4></div><div id="collapse1" class="panel-collapse collapse in" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading1"><div class="panel-body"><p>The 1stPayPOS is very competitively priced and we provide a wide range of payment options from outright purchase to leasing.</p></div></div></div><div class="panel panel-default"><div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading2"><h4 class="panel-title"><a class="collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2">Can I transfer my existing inventory?</a></h4></div><div id="collapse2" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading2"><div class="panel-body"><p>As long as your inventory can be exported in the proper format. Be sure to ask your sales representative to verify this at your appointment.</p></div></div></div><div class="panel panel-default"><div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading3"><h4 class="panel-title"><a class="collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse3">Does the 1stPayPOS come with an iPad?</a></h4></div><div id="collapse3" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading3"><div class="panel-body"><p>The iPad is not provided with the system, but any iPad running iOS7 is compatible.</p></div></div></div><div class="panel panel-default"><div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading4"><h4 class="panel-title"><a class="collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse4">Is the 1stPayPOS system secure?</a></h4></div><div id="collapse4" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading4"><div class="panel-body"><p>The 1stPayPOS meets VISA/MC PCI compliance standards and encrypts all sensitive card data.</p></div></div></div><div class="panel panel-default"><div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading5"><h4 class="panel-title"><a class="collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse5">Is the 1stPayPOS system difficult to use?</a></h4></div><div id="collapse5" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading5"><div class="panel-body"><p>The 1stPayPOS is very user friendly. Also support and training will ensure that you are proficient with the system in short time.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><div class="contact-common"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12"><h2 class="h1 semi-bold" style="margin-bottom:4rem;">Get In Touch With Us &amp; Keep Your Business Running Smooth</h2></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4"><img src="/content/uploads/media/new-images/support.png" alt="Support"/><span class="heading">Support</span><p>24/7 Customer Service &amp; Technical Support For <span class="bold">Existing</span> Merchants</p><a title="Call Heritage Payment Solutions" href="tel:8007898897"><span>(800) 789-8897</span></a></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4"><div class="borders"><img src="/content/uploads/media/new-images/sales.png" alt="Sales"/><span class="heading">Sales</span><a title="Call Heritage Payment Solutions" href="tel:<?php echo $phone_link; ?>"><span>Phone: <?php echo $phone; ?></span></a><a title="Fax Heritage Payment Solutions" href="tel:8884547069"><span>Fax: 888-454-7069</span></a><a title="Email Heritage Payment Solutions" href="mailto:Terry.r@heritageps.net"><span>Email: Terry.r@heritageps.net</span></a></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4"><img src="/content/uploads/media/new-images/address.png" alt="Address"/><span class="heading">Address</span><p>616 Dr. Calvin Jones Hwy. Suite 100<br>Wake Forest, NC 27587</p><a href="https://goo.gl/maps/9R1XTcu5PXs" title="Get Directions" target="_blank"><span>View the Map</span></a></div></div></div></div></section><?php include $_SERVER["DOCUMENT_ROOT"] . "/includes/footer.php"; ?>